properties.comment_project: Drinking Fountains  Currently switch off due to Covid. We are awaiting government guidance to inform re-opening. If this is provided by June and there are no additional costs/considerations or other variables preventing re-opening the facilities should be available. Toilets  Each block has accessible toilets and baby changing facilities available Indoor Spaces - Parks have a number of buildings/rooms that the public can use. However, charges apply and advance booking is required. There are a lot of open and green spaces in Southwark that are high quality and well maintained spaces but do not have toliets and water fountains so do not meet the criteria but could be cool sites. See the Southwark website for more details: Southwark.gov.uk/parks-and-open-spaces
